The AI-enabled Smart Parking System is designed to improve parking efficiency by using artificial intelligence to detect and manage parking spaces. Traditional parking systems are time-consuming and often lead to traffic congestion. This system uses image processing and machine learning techniques to identify available and occupied parking slots in real time. It provides accurate parking information to users, reducing search time and fuel consumption. The system enhances urban mobility, optimizes space utilization, and offers a smarter, automated parking solution.
